### 測試會員列表API
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users?page=1&limit=10
Cookie: [管理員登入cookie]

### 測試搜尋會員
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users?search=公司&page=1&limit=10
Cookie: [管理員登入cookie]

### 測試狀態篩選
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users?status=ACTIVE&page=1&limit=10
Cookie: [管理員登入cookie]

### 測試排序
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users?sortBy=points&sortOrder=desc&page=1&limit=10
Cookie: [管理員登入cookie]

### 測試會員詳情API
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users/[會員ID]
Cookie: [管理員登入cookie]

### 測試更新會員狀態
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users/[會員ID]
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: [管理員登入cookie]

{
  "status": "SUSPENDED",
  "reason": "違反使用條款"
}

### 測試更新會員資訊
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users/[會員ID]
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: [管理員登入cookie]

{
  "contactPerson": "張三",
  "phone": "0912345678"
}

### 測試點數調整（增加）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users/[會員ID]/points
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: [管理員登入cookie]

{
  "amount": 100,
  "reason": "活動獎勵",
  "type": "ADD"
}

### 測試點數調整（減少）
